Console Christmas Tree

This program was written for fun to simply draw a Christmas Tree on the console.

Compiling:

make

Running:

./xmastree

Running the command with no arguments as provided above will draw a tree with a
length of 7.

./xmastree <length>

Running the command with a length will draw the tree to the specified length.
The length must range between 5-31. It must step up by two starting from 5. For
example 5, 7, 9, 11, 13, ... 31.

